Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天上到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要去波瓦提耶對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是要去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃蛋糕不會長高的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要不要去\N蛋糕吃到飽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽同學這麼早就有班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，你也是在那裡打工嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟日暮一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那樣子笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗晴空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然飛揚落下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:02:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.31,0:02:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第5話 雨一一 。 淚水……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的便當總是很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是早上跟媽媽一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起撐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送妳到教會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨傘…喔，下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經進入梅雨季節了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨鋒線仍在往北前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜到明天之間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會穿越日本海這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深優是葛瑞爾神父的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬瑟夫 ． 葛瑞爾\N是我正式的養父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教會應該在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右斜前方有路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,300公尺後左轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去海邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索性就去沖繩一趟如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧，真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了一場夏日的回憶\N兩個人攜手努力打工是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是來吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼探望勤勞少女，就通通來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說鴇羽巧海是妳弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的跟尾久崎晶\N住同一間宿舍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次聽說耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子沒錯啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽舞衣同學，妳不瞭解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校園第一美少年的晶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟目前受喜愛的程度\N急速上升中的鴇羽巧海兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同一個房間同睡同起耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有兩個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論早晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.14,0:05:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!可不可以別把我家弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖進奇怪的世界裡面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我所知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是不用擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，晶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晚餐煮太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還燒什麼飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在想些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩進我的地盤裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，你要不要一起吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我～就～說～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是難搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很希望他們好好相處的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.25,0:05:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過晶很可愛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，鴇羽同學\N妳喜歡唱KTV嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有到明天截止的免費券
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起？反正明天放假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從早上就要來這裡上班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉!下次也要找我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她賺這麼多錢要做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣一定有她的原因在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別追究這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!妳是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚…肚子…好餓…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼要一直等我回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是有教過妳\N怎麼買學生餐廳的食券嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣煮的飯比較好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍…拍馬屁也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會給妳加菜的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子為什麼總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來之後會弄晚飯給妳吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午飯妳自己想辦法解決
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來呢？跟晶處得好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種前途多難的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過漸漸地熟絡起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？看來是不用擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也習慣這個班級了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宿舍這邊\N神崎學長等人也很照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都過得很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有帶介紹函嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要記得跟移植協調師\N好好打個招呼喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事應該在\N來到這間學校之前就說好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還想講
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就把你到幾歲\N都還跟我一起洗澡的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洩漏出去唷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，打工打工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.95,0:09:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？澤田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去跟關係不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國醫院那邊問看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬事拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生，國道上\N似乎有公車發生車禍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分鐘後會進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海，今天就先這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤田老師的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到新聞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說傷得很重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那班公車，小茜也常搭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到新聞真的很擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師是住你家的醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照爸爸的說法是\N雖然沒有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要住院一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤田老師年紀也不小了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？臉色很難看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才早上喔，振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有嗎？我沒事啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天午飯到自助餐廳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會帶命一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是那個做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊的人\N有出來負責收拾殘局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，澤田老師還真倒楣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也已經處理完畢\N現在轉進一般的醫院了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無依者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認有戰鬥過的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是新的HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:10:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也會加以妥善處理的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡茶，請稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，二三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然說這是HiME的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們真的是強迫她們去面對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘酷的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命，不可以弄掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃掉了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說可以去探病了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女生就由我們作代表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有楯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他剛剛還在那邊耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來就是跟大家講一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是別的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽同學是不是\N有個弟弟還是什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊，叫做巧海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，果真如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪她要這麼賣力打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧海他？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要帶鮮花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有水果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及冷茶對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有交通費
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們今天有沒有空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好去唱個歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好？\N今天要把之前的份一口氣唱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天也有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣，真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦，我突然約也有不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏今天就剛好\N葵她們也有社團活動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺出了緊張的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實已經是老手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點，不然會賣完
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會賣完喔？\N對啊，快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有排到假是好事\N不過竟然找不到事情可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定不要再有所牽扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼又…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟著前面那輛公車
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公車？\N對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這些錢可以到得了的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.38,0:14:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，到這裡就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人，找錢!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有妳的東西!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖我同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，讓牠跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作真是迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是隸屬於\N被稱作"一番地"組織的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他們將HiME聚集到學園
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後那些救護車是幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.33,0:15:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被送到\N跟那些人有掛勾的醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後進行" 處理"\N讓他們忘記自己看到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧？怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N妳是怎麼看待自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但身為HiME的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是置身在這樣的現實之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪見台四已經把傷患運走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一名傷患
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇…鴇羽同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會沒跟這傢伙講\N要來探望澤田老師的事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說要全班湊錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼年代了還搞排擠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是，又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們聽說了…巧海的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得妳…一定很辛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會…知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…就是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心聽到爸爸他們的談話\N然後就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得很難啟齒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才剛轉進來沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得也不好給她增加負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要說抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還害妳們還特地為我著想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意原諒我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:18:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說沒有什麼\N原諒不原諒的吧!對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過鴇羽同學好偉大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要借筆記或考試重點的話\N要記得說喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔，舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的，真的會為妳加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸剛剛已經來接走巧海了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣真是棒，總是這麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊姊會替妳加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼，妳還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去跟以前\N叨擾過的醫生打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒帶傘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不讓妳撐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰希罕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可敬謝不敏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨傘而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫妳等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想也知道是開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是撐個傘，何必…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱的比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳以為現在幾月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想說點任性的話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種突然想大哭一場的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有碰過這種情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會說些話嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我加油之類的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"加油"這種話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是說的人還是聽的人\N都很不負責任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠拼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…所以該怎麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳一罐咖啡應該就夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是一罐冰咖啡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我是酷男啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊？酷男？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔～原來你很酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳給我差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唷，哥哥早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著啊!喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯，早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不像某人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會勉強自己裝酷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣果然是舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是廢話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，走了喔，命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」\N這句話我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.54,0:22:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:23:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 請你好好記著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要收藏在心底就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life\N總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼\N現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.14,0:23:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.76,0:23:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒十七歲（^^;）\N梅雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒十七歲（^^;）\N連日雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.83,0:23:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒十七歲（^^;）\N淚雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.26,0:23:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.83,0:23:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭下雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.47,0:23:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣妳怎麼了？振作點\N簡直就像我的眼淚一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋發霉了嗎\N從沒有雨傘的我臉上滑落的雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.34,0:23:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨天確實令人討厭\N那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:24:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣不在的時候\N我踏上尋找兄長的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪著我的是蘭丸和三毛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.95,0:24:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠們是這附近的野貓老大們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.59,0:24:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校很大，市鎮更大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到很多\N在跟阿爺一起住的山上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.23,0:24:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所看不到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.86,0:24:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.87,0:24:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.00,0:24:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很好吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很難吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都很難得一見
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都令人驚奇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厭捲了的話\N就跟蘭丸牠們一起玩捉迷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.44,0:24:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄來飄去的裙子很礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.08,0:24:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候可是\N全身光溜溜地在山裡面奔跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.65,0:24:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，如果在這邊做一樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.19,0:24:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被舞衣臭罵一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.09,0:24:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩累了就睡午覺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.69,0:24:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭丸跟三毛\N也會和我一起縮成一團睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.29,0:24:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了，不過我會忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.30,0:24:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為舞衣燒的飯在等我回去吃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.43,0:24:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長，我過得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.30,0:24:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長也有在找我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.11,0:24:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天可以見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.78,0:25:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是不是啊？兄長
